Package: modelrunnR
Title: Orchestrate R and Python Model Runs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jesse", "Brandt", , "jesse.a.brandt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Orchestrates R and Python model runs via lightweight
    configuration and a common harness interface. Inspired by the
    orchestration layer of the panelmodeler package.
